<div class="page-eyebrow">Protocol Guide</div>
  <h1>How to optimize<br>testosterone naturally &#8212;<br><em>what the evidence actually shows.</em></h1>
  <p class="guide-hero-sub">Testosterone declines roughly 1 to 2% per year after age 30, and by 40 the effects are measurable &#8212; in muscle mass, energy, libido, and metabolic health. This guide covers every evidence-based intervention that actually moves the needle, plus when natural optimization isn&#8217;t enough.</p>
</section>

